<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Staging Shield · {{.Env.EnvironmentName}} · {{.Env.Timestamp.Format "2006-01-02"}}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0f1419;
    --bg-card: #1a212b;
    --bg-card-2: #232b37;
    --border: #2c3644;
    --text: #e6edf3;
    --text-dim: #9aa6b2;
    --accent: #4f9cf9;
    --good: #3fb950;
    --warn: #d29922;
    --bad: #f85149;
    --critical: #ff5e5e;
    --high: #f85149;
    --med: #d29922;
    --low: #8b9aa8;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px; }
  header { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  header h1 { margin: 0 0 4px; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; }
  header h1 .pill { font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
  header .meta { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13px; }
  header .meta span { margin-right: 16px; }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .card h2 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; color: var(--text); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 8px; }

  .global-score {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;
  }
  .score-num {
    font-size: 56px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1;
  }
  .score-num.score-good { color: var(--good); }
  .score-num.score-warn { color: var(--warn); }
  .score-num.score-bad  { color: var(--bad); }
  .score-of { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; }

  .aptitud {
    padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .aptitud.apto    { background: rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.12); color: var(--good); border: 1px solid rgba(63,185,80,0.3); }
  .aptitud.no-apto { background: rgba(248, 81, 73, 0.12); color: var(--bad);  border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,0.3); }
  .aptitud .label { font-size: 18px; }
  .aptitud .desc  { font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-dim); margin-left: 8px; font-size: 13px; }

  .domain-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 100px 80px 200px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .domain-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .domain-name { font-weight: 500; }
  .domain-score { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; text-align: right; }
  .domain-score.score-good { color: var(--good); }
  .domain-score.score-warn { color: var(--warn); }
  .domain-score.score-bad  { color: var(--bad); }
  .bar-wrap {
    height: 8px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bar-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 4px; }
  .bar-fill.score-good { background: var(--good); }
  .bar-fill.score-warn { background: var(--warn); }
  .bar-fill.score-bad  { background: var(--bad); }
  .domain-counts { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); text-align: right; }
  .domain-counts span { display: inline-block; margin-left: 8px; }
  .domain-counts .c-pass    { color: var(--good); }
  .domain-counts .c-partial { color: var(--warn); }
  .domain-counts .c-fail    { color: var(--bad); }
  .domain-counts .c-pend    { color: var(--text-dim); }

  section { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  section > h2 {
    font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 16px;
    padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  section > h2 .count { color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; margin-left: 8px; }

  .rule {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--border);
  }
  .rule.high     { border-left-color: var(--high); }
  .rule.med      { border-left-color: var(--med); }
  .rule.low      { border-left-color: var(--low); }
  .rule.critical { border-left-color: var(--critical); background: rgba(255, 94, 94, 0.05); }

  .rule-head {
    display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rule-id {
    font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: var(--bg-card-2);
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .rule-criterion { font-weight: 500; flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
  .rule-meta {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rule-meta span { padding: 2px 0; }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .badge.high     { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.18);  color: #ff8a82; }
  .badge.med      { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.18); color: #f0b945; }
  .badge.low      { background: rgba(139,154,168,0.18); color: var(--low); }
  .badge.pass     { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.18);  color: var(--good); }
  .badge.partial  { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.18); color: #f0b945; }
  .badge.fail     { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.18);  color: #ff8a82; }
  .badge.missing  { background: rgba(79,156,249,0.18); color: var(--accent); }
  .badge.manual   { background: rgba(154,166,178,0.18); color: var(--text-dim); }
  .badge.critical { background: rgba(255,94,94,0.25);  color: var(--critical); border: 1px solid rgba(255,94,94,0.5); }

  .evidence {
    background: var(--bg-card-2); border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .evidence .label { color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 600; margin-right: 6px; }
  .notes {
    margin-top: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); font-style: italic;
  }

  table.discovery-table {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px;
  }
  table.discovery-table th, table.discovery-table td {
    text-align: left; padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  table.discovery-table th { color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  table.discovery-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

  .recos { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .recos li {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    background: var(--bg-card-2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
  details summary { cursor: pointer; padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 500; }
  details summary:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  code { font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; background: var(--bg-card-2); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 12px; }

  /* ====== Centro de revisión manual ====== */
  .review-center {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79,156,249,0.08), rgba(79,156,249,0.02));
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,156,249,0.3);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .review-center h2 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 16px; }
  .review-center .subtitle { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .review-center .progress-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .progress-bar {
    flex: 1; min-width: 200px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--bg-card-2); border-radius: 5px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%; background: var(--accent);
    transition: width 0.25s ease-out;
  }
  .progress-text { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }
  .progress-text .muted { color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 400; }

  .review-actions {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .btn {
    background: var(--bg-card-2);
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 7px 14px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  .btn.primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .btn.primary:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); color: #fff; }
  .btn.ghost { background: transparent; }

  .toast {
    position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px;
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 12px 18px; border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    color: var(--text); font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;
    transform: translateY(8px); transition: all 0.2s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
  }
  .toast.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); pointer-events: auto; }
  .toast.success { border-color: var(--good); }
  .toast.error   { border-color: var(--bad); }

  /* ====== Controles de revisión manual por regla ====== */
  .review-controls {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
    background: var(--bg-card-2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--border);
  }
  .review-controls .rc-label {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px; display: block;
  }
  .verdict-row {
    display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .verdict-btn {
    flex: 1; min-width: 110px;
    padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px;
  }
  .verdict-btn:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--text-dim); }
  .verdict-btn.active.cumple   { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.15);  color: var(--good); border-color: var(--good); }
  .verdict-btn.active.parcial  { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.15); color: var(--warn); border-color: var(--warn); }
  .verdict-btn.active.nocumple { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.15);  color: var(--bad);  border-color: var(--bad); }
  .verdict-btn.active.naplica  { background: rgba(154,166,178,0.15); color: var(--text-dim); border-color: var(--text-dim); }

  .review-controls textarea {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px;
    resize: vertical; min-height: 50px;
  }
  .review-controls textarea:focus {
    outline: none; border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .rule.reviewed { border-left-color: var(--accent); }
  .reviewed-tag {
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(79,156,249,0.12);
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,156,249,0.35);
  }

  /* ====== Tabla de archivos .env ====== */
  .env-state-tag {
    display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .env-state-tag.tracked    { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.18);  color: #ff8a82; }
  .env-state-tag.history    { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.18);  color: #ff8a82; }
  .env-state-tag.gitignored { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.18);  color: var(--good); }
  .env-state-tag.notignored { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.18); color: var(--warn); }

  /* ====== Flash animation para cambios de score/cobertura ======
     Se activa al aplicar veredictos manuales o al importar revisión, para
     que el usuario perciba claramente que los porcentajes recalcularon. */
  @keyframes flash-update {
    0%   { background-color: rgba(79,156,249,0.55); }
    35%  { background-color: rgba(79,156,249,0.35); }
    100% { background-color: transparent; }
  }
  .flash {
    animation: flash-update 1s ease-out;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* ====== Sección de SVR cumplidas con evidencia (transparencia) ====== */
  .passed-domain-block {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .passed-domain-block > h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--good);
    padding-left: 10px;
  }
  .passed-domain-block > h3 .ds-mini {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-left: 8px;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .domain-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .domain-counts { text-align: left; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<header>
  <h1>Staging Shield <span class="pill">{{.Env.EnvironmentType}}</span></h1>
  <div class="meta">
    <span><strong>Entorno:</strong> {{.Env.EnvironmentName}}</span>
    <span><strong>Stack:</strong> {{.Env.StackType}}</span>
    <span><strong>Objetivo:</strong> {{.Env.Target}}</span>
    {{if .Env.IPAddress}}<span><strong>IP:</strong> {{.Env.IPAddress}}</span>{{end}}
    <span><strong>Evaluado:</strong> {{.Env.Timestamp.Format "2006-01-02 15:04:05"}}</span>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="grid">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Security Score Global</h2>
    <div class="global-score">
      <div id="global-score-num" class="score-num {{if ge .Stats.GlobalScore 80.0}}score-good{{else if ge .Stats.GlobalScore 60.0}}score-warn{{else}}score-bad{{end}}">
        <span id="global-score-value">{{printf "%.1f" .Stats.GlobalScore}}</span><span class="score-of"> / 100</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13px;">Reglas evaluadas: <span id="evaluated-count">{{.Stats.EvaluatedRules}}</span> / {{.Stats.TotalRules}}</div>
        <div style="color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13px;">Cobertura total: <span id="coverage-value">{{printf "%.1f" .Stats.Coverage}}</span>%</div>
        <div style="color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px;">
          (auto: <span id="auto-coverage">{{printf "%.1f" .Stats.AutoCoverage}}</span>% ·
          manual: <span id="manual-coverage">{{printf "%.1f" .Stats.ManualCoverage}}</span>%)
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Aptitud para promoción</h2>
    <div id="aptitud-box" class="aptitud {{if .Stats.Apto}}apto{{else}}no-apto{{end}}">
      {{if .Stats.Apto}}
        <span class="label">✓ APTO</span>
        <span class="desc" id="aptitud-desc">No hay SVR críticas en estado 'no cumple'.</span>
      {{else}}
        <span class="label">✗ NO APTO</span>
        <span class="desc" id="aptitud-desc">Existen {{len .Stats.CriticalFailures}} regla(s) crítica(s) en estado 'no cumple'.</span>
      {{end}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
  <h2>Score por dominio</h2>
  {{range .DomainList}}
  <div class="domain-row" data-domain="{{.Name}}">
    <div class="domain-name">{{.Name}}</div>
    <div class="bar-wrap">
      <div class="bar-fill {{.BadgeCls}}" data-bar style="width: {{.BarPct}}%"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="domain-score {{.BadgeCls}}" data-domain-score>{{.ScoreStr}}</div>
    <div class="domain-counts">
      <span class="c-pass" data-c-pass>✓ {{.Cumple}}</span>
      <span class="c-partial" data-c-partial>◐ {{.Parcial}}</span>
      <span class="c-fail" data-c-fail>✗ {{.NoCumple}}</span>
      <span class="c-pend" data-c-pend>? {{.NoEval}}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{end}}
</div>

{{if or .ManualView .NoEvidenceView}}
<div class="review-center">
  <h2>Centro de revisión manual</h2>
  <div class="subtitle">
    {{len .ManualView}} regla(s) requieren revisión humana y {{len .NoEvidenceView}} no pudieron evaluarse automáticamente por falta de datos. Marque cada una directamente desde su tarjeta y la cobertura, el score por dominio y el score global se actualizarán al instante. Cuando termine, exporte un archivo de revisión para que las próximas corridas no pierdan estos veredictos.
  </div>
  <div class="progress-row">
    <div class="progress-text">
      <span id="manual-progress-current">0</span><span class="muted"> / </span><span id="manual-progress-total">{{.ManualSlotsTotal}}</span>
      <span class="muted"> reglas pendientes evaluadas manualmente</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-bar">
      <div id="manual-progress-fill" class="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="review-actions">
    <button class="btn primary" id="btn-export-review">⬇ Exportar revisión (YAML)</button>
    <label class="btn" for="file-import-review">⬆ Importar revisión</label>
    <input type="file" id="file-import-review" accept=".yaml,.yml,.json" style="display:none">
    <button class="btn ghost" id="btn-reset-review">Limpiar veredictos</button>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim);">
    El archivo exportado puede pasarse a la CLI con <code>staging-shield scan --review revision.yaml</code> para conservar los veredictos en la próxima corrida.
  </div>
</div>
{{end}}

{{define "ruleCard"}}
<div class="rule {{.SevClass}}{{if .Critical}} critical{{end}}"
     data-rule-id="{{.ID}}"
     data-domain="{{.Domain}}"
     data-severity="{{.SevWeight}}"
     data-critical="{{if .Critical}}true{{else}}false{{end}}"
     data-initial-status="{{.StatusKey}}"
     data-can-review="{{if .CanReview}}true{{else}}false{{end}}">
  <div class="rule-head">
    <span class="rule-id">{{.ID}}</span>
    <span class="badge {{.SevClass}}">{{.Severity}}</span>
    <span class="badge {{.StatusCls}}" data-status-badge>{{.Status}}</span>
    {{if .Critical}}<span class="badge critical">crítica</span>{{end}}
    <span class="reviewed-tag" data-reviewed-tag style="display:none">revisado manualmente</span>
    <span class="rule-criterion">{{.Criterion}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="rule-meta">
    <span>Dominio: {{.Domain}}</span>
    <span>Referencia: <code>{{.Reference}}</code></span>
    <span>Modo: {{.Mode}}</span>
  </div>
  {{if .Evidence}}<div class="evidence"><span class="label">Evidencia:</span>{{.Evidence}}</div>{{end}}
  {{if .Notes}}<div class="notes" data-notes>↳ {{.Notes}}</div>{{end}}

  {{if .CanReview}}
  <div class="review-controls" data-review-controls>
    <span class="rc-label">Veredicto del evaluador</span>
    <div class="verdict-row" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Veredicto manual para {{.ID}}">
      <button type="button" class="verdict-btn" data-verdict="cumple"   data-rule-target="{{.ID}}">✓ Cumple</button>
      <button type="button" class="verdict-btn" data-verdict="parcial"  data-rule-target="{{.ID}}">◐ Cumple parcialmente</button>
      <button type="button" class="verdict-btn" data-verdict="nocumple" data-rule-target="{{.ID}}">✗ No cumple</button>
      <button type="button" class="verdict-btn" data-verdict="naplica"  data-rule-target="{{.ID}}">○ No aplica</button>
    </div>
    <textarea data-evidence-input
              placeholder="Evidencia / justificación del veredicto (opcional pero recomendado: documento de referencia, número de ticket, fecha de validación, persona consultada)"></textarea>
  </div>
  {{end}}
</div>
{{end}}

{{if .CriticalView}}
<section>
  <h2>SVR críticas que bloquean la promoción <span class="count">({{len .CriticalView}})</span></h2>
  {{range .CriticalView}}{{template "ruleCard" .}}{{end}}
</section>
{{end}}

{{if .Recommendations}}
<section>
  <h2>Recomendaciones priorizadas</h2>
  <ul class="recos">
    {{range .Recommendations}}<li>{{.}}</li>{{end}}
  </ul>
</section>
{{end}}

{{if .FailedView}}
<section>
  <h2>Hallazgos: SVR en estado "no cumple" <span class="count">({{len .FailedView}})</span></h2>
  {{range .FailedView}}{{template "ruleCard" .}}{{end}}
</section>
{{end}}

{{if .NoEvidenceView}}
<section>
  <h2>Reglas con evidencia incompleta <span class="count">({{len .NoEvidenceView}})</span></h2>
  <p style="color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 12px;">
    Estas reglas no se pudieron evaluar automáticamente porque la configuración del programa cliente no incluye los datos necesarios. Use los controles de cada tarjeta para registrar el veredicto si dispone de la evidencia por otra vía: al hacerlo entrarán al cálculo del score y subirán la cobertura.
  </p>
  {{range .NoEvidenceView}}{{template "ruleCard" .}}{{end}}
</section>
{{end}}

{{if .ManualView}}
<section>
  <h2>Reglas que requieren revisión manual <span class="count">({{len .ManualView}})</span></h2>
  <p style="color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 12px;">
    Requieren revisión documental, validación organizacional o acceso administrativo que el programa cliente no tiene. Marque cada una con su veredicto y la cobertura del modelo subirá en consecuencia.
  </p>
  {{range .ManualView}}{{template "ruleCard" .}}{{end}}
</section>
{{end}}

{{if .PassedView}}
<section>
  <h2>SVR que cumplen y su evidencia <span class="count">({{len .PassedView}} reglas — sustento del Security Score)</span></h2>
  <p style="color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 16px;">
    Esta sección lista todas las reglas que el motor automático o un veredicto manual marcaron como <strong style="color: var(--good);">Cumple</strong> o <strong style="color: var(--warn);">Cumple parcialmente</strong>. La evidencia mostrada al pie de cada tarjeta es exactamente la que el modelo usó para subir el score: si la evidencia no convence al evaluador, el veredicto puede sobreescribirse desde los controles de la tarjeta o vía archivo de revisión.
  </p>
  {{range .PassedByDomain}}
  <div class="passed-domain-block">
    <h3>{{.Name}} <span class="ds-mini">— {{len .Rules}} regla(s) cumplen</span></h3>
    {{range .Rules}}{{template "ruleCard" .}}{{end}}
  </div>
  {{end}}
</section>
{{end}}

